<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>Taepyung Company Profile - 06</title>

  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4 landscape;
      margin: 0;
    }

    :root {
      --green: #387040;
      --light-green: #70C088;
      --cream: #F7F5EF;
      --black: #111111;
      --gray: #777777;
      --line: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
      background: #d9d9d9;
      color: var(--black);
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      print-color-adjust: exact;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      width: 297mm;
      height: 210mm;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20mm 22mm 16mm;
      background: var(--cream);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Header */
    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      height: 14mm;
      margin-bottom: 18mm;
    }

    .logo-area {
      width: 42mm;
      height: 12mm;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.35);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .logo-area img {
      width: 100%;
      max-height: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
    }

    .doc-label {
      padding-top: 1mm;
      font-size: 8px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--gray);
      text-align: right;
    }

    /* Main Layout */
    .layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.82fr 1.18fr;
      gap: 22mm;
      height: 128mm;
    }

    .left,
    .right {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .left {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 8.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 9mm;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 1.16;
      letter-spacing: -0.065em;
      font-weight: 760;
    }

    .lead {
      margin-top: 12mm;
      max-width: 84mm;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.85;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      color: #222;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .story-copy {
      margin-top: 7mm;
      max-width: 86mm;
      font-size: 10.6px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #4a4a4a;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Bottom Brand Block */
    .brand-box {
      width: 82mm;
      border-top: 1.5px solid var(--green);
      padding-top: 5.5mm;
    }

    .brand-name {
      font-size: 25px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 780;
      margin-bottom: 4mm;
    }

    .brand-text {
      max-width: 70mm;
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Right Side */
    .brand-visual {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: 58mm;
      margin-bottom: 6mm;
      background: var(--green);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .brand-visual img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    .brand-visual-placeholder {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
      font-size: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .brand-word {
      position: absolute;
      left: 8mm;
      bottom: 7mm;
      font-size: 34px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.07em;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 780;
    }

    .meaning-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 5mm;
    }

    .meaning-card {
      min-height: 62mm;
      padding: 7mm;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .meaning-index {
      font-size: 8px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
    }

    .meaning-title {
      margin: 0 0 4mm;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.18;
      letter-spacing: -0.055em;
      font-weight: 760;
    }

    .meaning-desc {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 9.7px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .quote-strip {
      margin-top: 6mm;
      padding: 5mm 6mm;
      background: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.16);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 10mm;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .quote-strip strong {
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.35;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 760;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .quote-strip span {
      font-size: 9.5px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      left: 22mm;
      right: 22mm;
      bottom: 9mm;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: var(--gray);
    }

    .footer-logo {
      font-weight: 750;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--green);
    }

    .page-no {
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.65);
    }

    @media print {
      html,
      body {
        width: 297mm;
        height: 210mm;
        background: #fff;
      }

      .page {
        margin: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <section class="page">

    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="logo-area">
        LOGO
        <!-- 로고 넣을 때 -->
        <!-- <img src="assets/taepyung-logo-green.svg" alt="Taepyung"> -->
      </div>

      <div class="doc-label">
        Company Profile<br />
        Ver. 2025-V1
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="layout">

      <section class="left">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Brand Story</div>

          <h1>
            브론디는<br />
            평범한 일상을 위한<br />
            생활 위생지 브랜드입니다
          </h1>

          <p class="lead">
            브론디는 누구나 안심하고 사용할 수 있는 제품을 지향하며,
            오랫동안 사랑받는 생활 위생지 브랜드가 되고자 하는 마음을 담고 있습니다.
          </p>

          <p class="story-copy">
            매일 사용하는 제품일수록 과장된 특별함보다 변함없는 편안함이 중요합니다.
            브론디는 일상 가까이에 놓이는 제품으로서, 친근하고 안정적인 사용 경험을 만들어갑니다.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="brand-box">
          <div class="brand-name">Blondy</div>
          <div class="brand-text">
            평범한 사람들의 일상 속에서 오래 사랑받는 화장지가 되고자 하는 의미를 담았습니다.
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="right">

        <div class="brand-visual">
          <div class="brand-visual-placeholder">
            BRAND IMAGE AREA
          </div>

          <!-- 브랜드 이미지 넣을 때 -->
          <!-- <img src="assets/blondy-brand-image.jpg" alt="Blondy Brand"> -->

          <div class="brand-word">Blondy</div>
        </div>

        <div class="meaning-grid">

          <div class="meaning-card">
            <div>
              <div class="meaning-index">01</div>
              <h3 class="meaning-title">Everyday</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="meaning-desc">
              화장지는 누구나 매일 사용하는 제품입니다.
              브론디는 일상 속에서 자연스럽게 함께하는 브랜드를 지향합니다.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="meaning-card">
            <div>
              <div class="meaning-index">02</div>
              <h3 class="meaning-title">Friendly</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="meaning-desc">
              부담스럽지 않고 친근한 이미지로,
              가족과 가정의 생활 가까이에 놓이는 제품 경험을 만듭니다.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="meaning-card">
            <div>
              <div class="meaning-index">03</div>
              <h3 class="meaning-title">Long-loved</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="meaning-desc">
              일시적인 유행보다 오랫동안 신뢰받는 품질과 사용감을 통해
              꾸준히 선택받는 브랜드를 목표로 합니다.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="quote-strip">
          <strong>For ordinary days</strong>
          <span>
            브론디는 평범한 일상에 필요한 부드러움과 안정감을 전하는 생활 위생지 브랜드입니다.
          </span>
        </div>

      </section>

    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="footer-logo">TAE PYEONG PAPER</div>
      <div class="page-no">06</div>
    </footer>

  </section>

</body>
</html>
